State Farm is the largest auto insurance company in the country in terms of direct premiums written.﻿﻿ Founded in 1922, the company offers a wide range of insurance products, including motorcycle, motor home, homeowners, renter’s, and life insurance.
 
With robust coverage options and multiple discounts, State Farm is known for customer service. It has more than 19,000 insurance agents nationwide and commands more than 16% of the private passenger auto insurance market share.
 Multiple policy discounts available Strong third-party ratings Useful mobile app Must submit personal information to get a quote Agent responsiveness variable Rideshare insurance not available in all states 
